
### Auth
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api
@token = {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### Register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "name": "Test User",
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "password"
}

### Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "password"
}

### Me
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Menu Items
### Get All Menus (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu-items
Accept: application/json

### Create Menu (Auth, Multipart)
POST {{baseUrl}}/menu-items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

Nasi Goreng Spesial
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Nasi goreng dengan telur dan ayam
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

25000
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="nasigoreng.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./nasigoreng.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Get Menu Detail (Public)
@menuId = 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu-items/{{menuId}}
Accept: application/json

### Update Menu (Auth, Multipart)
# Note: For PHP Multipart PUT, use POST with _method=PUT
POST {{baseUrl}}/menu-items/{{menuId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="_method"

PUT
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

Nasi Goreng Seafood
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

30000
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Delete Menu
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/menu-items/{{menuId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
